  ('medical-tech-moex-20268', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-4222900d', 'sub-medical-tech-12', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關Chryseobacterium meningosepticum之特性，何者不正確？ 可引起新生兒腦膜炎敗血症  有運動性 可產生黃色色素    oxidase (＋)，indole (＋)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2bd1634fb6a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83395b9967fb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學(包括細菌與黴菌)", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20269', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-4222900d', 'sub-medical-tech-12', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Aeromonas hydrophilia 在EMB上所形成的菌落可能與E. coli相似，下列何者可區分？ oxidase test  運動性  溶血性  indole test', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2bd1634fb6a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83395b9967fb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學(包括細菌與黴菌)", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20270', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-4222900d', 'sub-medical-tech-12', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關MR/VP test 之敘述，何者正確？ 傳統的MR test培養48小時才能判讀，加methyl red試劑，呈紅色者為陽性 MR test陽性表示發酵glucose產生混合酸，pH 5.4以上 VP test 培養24 小時即可判讀，先加40% KOH，再加α-naphthol VP test 陽性表示glucose代謝產物中沒有acetoin', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2bd1634fb6a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "83395b9967fb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "4001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "微生物學及臨床微生物學(包括細菌與黴菌)", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
